{"tid":1564953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用中秋作為最新外國戰線諗唔諗得過？","createTime":"2019-09-13T03:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T05:23:00.000Z","uid":270111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c0e7f8fab851c6f62c2aae16eeeab4cd56e003f6","tid":1564953,"uid":270111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:16:14.000Z","msg":"首先精簡懶人包：將今日中秋既相放上Twitter比外國人睇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返工唔打太多，以下正文：<br />\n<br />\n外國其實一直好鍾意睇香港人既創意抗爭方法，流水革命個term仲傳埋出去，所以呢場運動先可以係外國一直keep到個熱度。<br />\n<br />\n早前既人鏈同最近既《願榮光歸香港》都好受外國關注，但係行程模式慢慢固定，好似主要都係呢兩樣野互相交疊，特別係藍絲唱國歌我地仲要同佢對唱，好似有少少比人牽住走咁。<br />\n<br />\n適逢今日中秋，係一個外國冇既節日，我地係過中秋既同時，如果可以順便做埋國際文宣，會唔會又帶黎一波話題呢？<br />\n<br />\n小弟有見到有各種創意燈籠月餅，以及切合時事既燈謎，呢d都係體現左香港富創意既一面，相當值得放上twitter比外國人睇。英文好既手足可以順便做埋燈謎翻譯，又或者講下月餅既革命故事。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter落tag都建議加個新tag，例如#HKMidAutumn之類。<br />\n<br />\n返工時間打唔到太多野，希望各位手足比d意見討論下work唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝大家中秋快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2f2d5181b52db7839073aafbb237b907dc3ec1","tid":1564953,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna